ie-bookshop-e-books.html</link><description>BookShop是一个可以独立，实体书店在线出售其书籍的网站，它正在启动一个应用程序，该应用程序也将允许销售电子书。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 19:43:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/28/books/indie-bookshop-e-books.html</guid></item><item><title>图书评论：史黛西·霍恩（Stacy Horn）</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/28/books/review/stacy-horn-killing-fields-of-east-new-york.html</link><description>在“东纽约的杀戮场”中，史黛西·霍恩（Stacy Horn）概述了1990年代的白领犯罪狂潮及其留下的残骸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 10:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/28/books/review/stacy-horn-killing-fields-of-east-new-york.html</guid></item><item><title>找到您的下一本书</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/what-to-read-next.html</link><description>从书籍评论编辑中阅读选秀者，保证适合任何心情。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/what-to-read-next.html</guid></item><item><title>2024年的10本最佳书籍</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/03/books/best-books-2024.html</link><description>《纽约时报》书评的工作人员选择了当年的小说和非小说。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/03/books/best-books-2024.html</guid></item><item><title>现在要读的最好的惊悚片</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/thriller-books.html</link><description>无论您是寻找经典还是最新，最伟大的，都可以从这里开始。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/thriller-books.html</guid></item><item><title>“美国历史学家院长”：肯·伯恩斯（Ken Burns）在威廉·E·莱克滕堡（William E.</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/29/us/ken-burns-on-william-e-leuchtenburg.html</link><description>一个是电影制片人，另一个是学术顾问（有时出现在相机上），两人成为亲密的朋友，一起工作了40多年。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/29/us/ken-burns-on-william-e-l